{"tid":2435113,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【47 人案】柯耀林宣布退出政治聯繫　不再參加各級選舉","createTime":"2021-03-06T04:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T04:22:01.000Z","uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5fc2318634f03c27ff07da5175b82e41968e3fbb","tid":2435113,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:11:38.000Z","msg":"47 名民主派人士被控「串謀顛覆」，大部分被告仍然未獲准保釋，繼續還押。被告之一、西頁區議員柯耀林的社交網站今（6 日）早更新，指收到柯透過福利官向代表律師傳話，發出公開聲明，即時退出所有政治聯繫及組織。<br />\n<br />\n此外，柯耀林決定不再參加香港各級選舉及任何政治選舉，包括立法會及區議會選舉。資料顯示，柯耀林現為「將軍澳民生關注組」主席。<br />\n<br />\n總裁判官、國安法指定法官蘇惠德周四（4 日）原本批准包括柯耀林在內的 15 人保釋，律政司隨即提覆核，眾人續還押。昨日律政司突撤銷楊雪盈、呂智恆、林景楠及劉偉聰覆核，4 人獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n其餘 11 人的保釋申請今在高等法院聆訊，控方申押後，高院法官、另一國安法指定法官杜麗冰已表明，今日不會批出臨時保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3957126857706238/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F3957126857706238%2F&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=b41fe338\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3957126857706238/</a><br />\n<br />\n認輸喇唔打喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177ae7bec3a96518d67a5a14afcdcb616c595033","tid":2435113,"uid":260722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:19:27.000Z","msg":"<del>剝奪</del>放棄政治權利<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa166f06d5a1547748edc482f27ec3bf47c2090","tid":2435113,"uid":300095,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T04:20:46.000Z","msg":"一尻二個無膽匪類，當日搞35+就義正辭嚴講到火裡火裡去水裡水裡去。"},{"pid":"0cfd5407209aed0fb01ac15f91d28ba4a81cef1d","tid":2435113,"